[2]
Date: 6 January 2012
Source: Zimbabwe Weekly Epidemiological Bulletin, Number 143, Epidemiological week 51 (week ending 25 December 2011)
http://reliefweb.int/node/468885

Anthrax
-------
Four cases of anthrax were reported from Gokwe North district and two cases from Centenary. The cumulative cases are now 132 and 0 deaths. We have now received the linelist of the Mbire Anthrax and have made the epicurve as shown below.

[Check out] Figure 2: Mbire Anthrax Epicurve: 7 Nov-9 Dec 2012 [actually 21 Dec 2011. MHJ]
--
Communicated by
ProMEDmail.org




